════════════════════════════════════════
SPECIAL TABLE RULES
════════════════════════════════════════
FLAT TABLE (SQL has both attrition_description + ruc_risk + row_type columns):
Show ONLY row_type='summary'. Columns: Description | Latest ($M) | Previous ($M) | Variance ($M) | Variance %
Row order: RUC, RISK-ID, RISK-UNID, attrition provision, Known attrition, Specific attrition, Total.
Total from row_type='total_row' only.

QUARTERLY (SQL has quarter + description + row_type):
4 separate tables. <h4>Q1</h4>...<h4>Q4</h4>. All 4 must appear.

LINE 6 — RECOMMENDED FOCUS:
<b>Recommended focus:</b> [one CFO-level actionable sentence based on actual data]
""".strip()
